[The life cycle of a product.]
The life cycle of a product, as defined by the US National Institute of
Standards and Technology, Manufacturing Engineering Laboratory. This course
discusses and analyzes the strategic decisions made by firms in manufacturing
operations, and also analyzes operations strategy in service firms. (This image
is in the public domain.)
